## 13. Risk Management

### 13.1 Risk Assessment Matrix

| Risk | Impact | Probability | Mitigation Strategy |
|------|--------|-------------|---------------------|
| **Incomplete/Poor Quality Datasets** | High | Medium | - Use multiple data sources<br>- Data validation pipeline<br>- Synthetic data generation as fallback |
| **Low Prediction Accuracy** | High | Medium | - Ensemble models<br>- Feature engineering<br>- Continuous model retraining<br>- Provide confidence scores |
| **API Rate Limits (External Data)** | Medium | High | - Cache external data<br>- Use free-tier APIs efficiently<br>- Batch requests<br>- Fallback to historical averages |
| **Scalability Issues** | Medium | Low | - Cloud-native architecture<br>- Containerization<br>- Auto-scaling<br>- Load testing |
| **Security Vulnerabilities** | High | Low | - Regular security audits<br>- Input validation<br>- Secure authentication<br>- Encryption |
| **User Adoption Challenges** | Medium | Medium | - Intuitive UI/UX<br>- User onboarding<br>- Marketing campaign<br>- Feedback collection |
| **Hackathon Time Constraints** | Medium | High | - Prioritize core features (MVP)<br>- Agile methodology<br>- Parallel workstreams<br>- Use pre-built libraries |
| **Model Drift Over Time** | Medium | Medium | - Automated monitoring<br>- Scheduled retraining<br>- A/B testing new models |
| **Dependency on External APIs** | Medium | Low | - Multiple data source options<br>- Graceful degradation<br>- Local fallbacks |
| **Privacy/Compliance Issues** | High | Low | - No PII collection<br>- GDPR compliance<br>- Transparent data usage<br>- Legal review |

### 13.2 Contingency Plans

**If Historical Data is Unavailable:**
- Generate synthetic datasets using statistical patterns
- Use public datasets from other cities as proxy
- Launch with limited zones where data exists

**If Model Accuracy is Below Target:**
- Deploy baseline statistical model (moving averages)
- Collect more data and retrain
- Adjust user expectations (wider confidence intervals)
- Provide historical trends as alternative

**If External APIs Fail:**
- Use cached data
- Fall back to manual event calendar
- Show reduced confidence scores
- Graceful degradation (core features still work)

**If User Adoption is Low:**
- Pivot messaging based on user feedback
- Add gamification elements
- Partner with parking operators for promotion
- Offer incentives (free premium period)

